    caption: [is absent in mammals. When arginine from dietary intake or protein turnover is insufficient for protein synthesis, the ornithine (cid:6)-aminotransferase reaction operates in the direction of ornithine formation. Ornithine is then converted to citrulline and arginine in the urea cycle.],
